title: Cal Smart Hoisin-Ginger Beef with Savoury Rice and Stir-Fried Veggies
description: This classic Southeast Asian-inspired combo of tender beef, savoury rice and spicy sauce is full of flavour but surprisingly light! Don't forget to drizzle the sauce over every bite.

